{"tid":794371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"夫婦結婚4年未孕 求醫揭妻是處女","createTime":"2018-08-26T07:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T14:56:53.000Z","uid":159074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98d407fe6f7a2f0f4eb1cf4004b66f586213652e","tid":794371,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/154130_38fa27d5b6dab7eccf9ddc35f20ed518.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F154130_38fa27d5b6dab7eccf9ddc35f20ed518.png&h=aa91cce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n性教育貧乏，不但未能讓人建立正確性觀念，有可能連男女基本生理結構都不懂而影響生育。中國貴州一對夫婦結婚4年一直未能懷孕，求醫後經醫生驗查，卻發現妻子仍是處女，但肛門容下3隻手指，原來夫婦一直把陰道和肛門位置弄錯，醫生向他們傳授正確性教育後，嫰妻終能成功懷孕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/227027/%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E8%B2%B4%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A4%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%AA%E5%AD%95-%E6%B1%82%E9%86%AB%E6%8F%AD%E5%A6%BB%E6%98%AF%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3-%E8%82%9B%E9%96%80%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B93%E6%8C%87?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F227027%2F%25E6%2590%259E%25E9%258C%25AF%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE-%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25AD%2595-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2586%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E8%2582%259B%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%25B93%25E6%258C%2587%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=9vfa5Gk%2F4M%2FCai7W1FCRxnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=27ea0b7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/227027/%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE-%E8%B2%B4%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%